<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stick-v">stick <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /stɪk/    美 /stɪk/  </p>
<p>(stuck, stuck)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(被) 刺入；(被) 戳进：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The nurse <strong>stuck</strong> the needle <strong>into</strong> my arm.
护士把针扎进我的手臂。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I found a nail <strong>sticking in</strong> the tyre.
我发现轮胎上扎了一根钉子。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>粘 (住)；贴 (住)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>stick a stamp on an envelope
在信封上贴邮票</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This food can <strong>stick to</strong> your teeth.
这种食物容易粘牙。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>伸出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Peter stuck his head behind the door.
彼得从门后探出头来。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>[非正式用语] 放置：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Stick your bags down there.
把你们的包搁在那儿吧。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>阻塞；(被) 难住：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The key has stuck in the lock.
钥匙卡在锁里了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was stuck by this question.
他被这个问题难住了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-get-stuck-in">be / get stuck in</h3>
<p>1.<strong>卡住；陷入：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They got stuck in a traffic jam.
他们遇到了交通堵塞。</p></div>

<h3 id="stick-around">stick around</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[非正式用语] 不走开；待在原地</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="stick-out">stick out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>伸出；突出：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Stick out your tongue, please.
请把舌头伸出来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The photo showed Edward with very short hair and his ears sticking out.
照片上，爱德华头发很短，双耳突出。</p></div>

<h3 id="stick-to">stick to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>坚持；遵守：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The surest way to success is sticking to your goal.
通向成功最可靠的方法是坚持目标。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Once he made a promise, he would stick to it (= he did as he had promised).
他一旦许下诺言，就会坚守这个诺言。</p></div>

<h3 id="stick-up">stick up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>竖立：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On Christmas morning we stuck up a board with “A Merry Christmas” on it.
在圣诞节的早上，我们竖起一块牌子，上面写着“圣诞快乐”。</p><footer>北师大⑧ – 24</footer></div>

<h3 id="stick-with">stick with</h3>
<p>1.<strong>持续；坚持：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You should choose an activity that you enjoy, and one that you’ll stick with.
你应该选择一项你喜欢并且会坚持下去的活动。</p><footer>2009 湖南改</footer></div>

<p>2.<strong>留在...的记忆里：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Those words will stick with me for the rest of my life.
我余生将永远记住这些话。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The cards had been <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (卡住) through the letterbox.  （2011 全国）  </li>
<li>Once a decision has been made, all of us should stick <strong><em>_</em></strong> it.  （2004 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. stuck  2. to  </p></div>